==English==

=== Etymology ===
from Greek (philosophia): philos = love + sophia = wisdom

=== Noun ===
'''philosophy'''  {{uncountable}}

# A comprehesive system of belief that is, generally, divided into five major subtopics:  [[Logic]]; [[Metaphysics]]; [[Epistemology]]; [[Ethics]] and [[Esthetics]]
# A general principle (usually moral)

